{"abstract": "A lawyer for the oil company questioned Steven R. Donziger in court about emails Chevron said supported its assertions of bribery and witness tampering in an Ecuadorean environmental case.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/20/business/energy-environment/chevron-assails-lawyer-who-led-multibillion-dollar-suit-against-it.html", "snippet": "A lawyer for the oil company questioned Steven R. Donziger in court about emails Chevron said supported its assertions of bribery and witness tampering in an Ecuadorean environmental case.", "lead_paragraph": "For two years Chevron has said that a multibillion-dollar judgment in a pollution case against the company in Ecuador was rigged by an American lawyer, Steven R. Donziger, asserting that he tampered with witnesses and bribed an Ecuadorean judge. On Tuesday, the company\u2019s lawyers confronted Mr. Donziger in a Manhattan federal courtroom.", "print_section": "B", "print_page": "2", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/11/20/business/DONZINGER/DONZINGER-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 392, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2013/11/20/business/DONZINGER/DONZINGER-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 392}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/11/20/business/DONZINGER/DONZINGER-jumbo.jpg", "height": 669, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/11/20/business/DONZINGER/DONZINGER-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1338, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2013/11/20/business/DONZINGER/